gantt
    title API Version Lifecycle Coexistence
    dateFormat  YYYY-MM-DD
    axisFormat  %b %Y

    section v1 lifecycle
    Design + pre-release review     :v1d,    2024-01-01, 90d
    Beta (private design partners)  :v1b,    after v1d, 90d
    GA (full support)               :active, v1ga,   after v1b, 540d
    Maintenance (security fixes)    :v1m,    after v1ga, 180d
    Deprecated (Sunset announced)   :crit,   v1dep,  after v1m, 360d
    Retired (410 Gone)              :v1r,    after v1dep, 90d

    section v2 lifecycle
    Design + pre-release review     :v2d,    2025-04-01, 90d
    Beta (parallel-run sandbox)     :v2b,    after v2d, 90d
    GA (full support)               :active, v2ga,   after v2b, 720d

    section Migration milestones
    Migration tooling published     :milestone, m1, 2025-10-01, 0d
    Sunset T-12 month notice        :milestone, m2, 2025-10-01, 0d
    Sunset T-6 month notice         :milestone, m3, 2026-04-01, 0d
    Sunset T-3 month notice         :milestone, m4, 2026-07-01, 0d
    Sunset T-1 month notice         :milestone, m5, 2026-09-01, 0d
    v1 sunset (binding date)        :milestone, m6, 2026-10-01, 0d

    section Retirement discipline
    Routes return 410 Gone          :r1, 2026-10-01, 30d
    Code removed from source repo   :r2, after r1, 30d
    Infrastructure destroyed        :r3, after r2, 30d
